dc_title_s: Map of the lands of the Michigan Land & Iron Co. Limited in the counties of Marquette, Baraga and Houghton, northern peninsula, Michigan.
dc_description_s: Also shows parts of Iron, Dickinson, and Menominee Counties. Includes inset of Grand Island. 1 map: col.; 86 x 70 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_creator_sm: Heliotype Printing Co.,Michigan Land & Iron Company.
